&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dataiku.com/?utm_source=newswire&amp;amp;utm_medium=press-release&amp;amp;utm_campaign=PlatformforAISuccess&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Dataiku&lt;/a&gt; is the Platform for AI Success, the enterprise orchestration layer for building, deploying, and governing AI. In a single environment, teams design and operate analytics, machine learning, and AI agents with the transparency, collaboration, and control enterprises require. Sitting above data platforms, cloud infrastructure, and AI services, Dataiku connects the full enterprise AI stack — empowering organizations to run AI across multi-vendor environments with centralized governance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The world’s leading companies rely on Dataiku to operationalize AI and run it as a true business performance engine delivering measurable value. For more, visit the Dataiku &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.dataiku.com/?_gl=1*17edvf4*_ga*MjA1Mjk5NzY4OC4xNjY3MjMyMDUz*_ga_B3YXRYMY48*MTY2OTA1MDY5NS4xMi4xLjE2NjkwNTA2OTguNTcuMC4w&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/dataiku/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/dataiku&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/dataiku&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an AI Healthcare &amp;amp; Life Science Solutions Consultant to join Dataiku’s Business Solutions department with a strong focus on supporting US business expansion. The role reports to the Health &amp;amp; Life Science Sr. Director. Your mission will be undertaken in close partnership with Dataiku’s broader Business Solutions team, including the Life Sciences Solution AI Engineers, as well as with Dataiku’s core teams: Sales, Customer, Partnership, Product and R&amp;amp;D.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will support three essential missions:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(1) Feed our strategic vision towards Healthcare &amp;amp; Life Sciences&lt;/strong&gt; and how to further accelerate&amp;nbsp; our growth in this industry. This will involve developing a deep understanding of Dataiku’s footprint, strong convictions as to analytics, ML and agent value for priority domains, current and target positioning in the ecosystem, and supporting the right plans to meet our ambitions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(2) Be a&amp;nbsp; Dataiku SME on Healthcare &amp;amp; Life Sciences&lt;/strong&gt;, and act as a gap bridger between precise industry needs, AI and Dataiku as a product. You will directly support clients and prospects as a trusted expert and support the development of the right assets and engagement support to boost GTM effectiveness in Life Sciences. In practice, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support sales and customer activities on Life Sciences: help customer dynamics understanding, act as a key spokesperson for prospects and customers, supporting executive engagement building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Articulate the specific value proposal of Dataiku for Life Sciences, and enable internal client facing teams in its articulating.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage the capitalization of internal knowledge and client experiences on Life Sciences (adoption stories, use-cases, …) and contribute to development of relevant material.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Boost Dataiku’s visibility on Life Sciences as an industry, as well as engage in the&amp;nbsp; execution of an impactful thought-leadership strategy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive high impact Customer Engagements with key decision makers in Healthcare &amp;amp; Life Sciences accounts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(3) Contribute to&amp;nbsp; the identification, scoping, and successful roll out of&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&qu

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dataiku.com/?utm_source=newswire&amp;amp;utm_medium=press-release&amp;amp;utm_campaign=PlatformforAISuccess&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Dataiku&lt;/a&gt; is the Platform for AI Success, the enterprise orchestration layer for building, deploying, and governing AI. In a single environment, teams design and operate analytics, machine learning, and AI agents with the transparency, collaboration, and control enterprises require. Sitting above data platforms, cloud infrastructure, and AI services, Dataiku connects the full enterprise AI stack — empowering organizations to run AI across multi-vendor environments with centralized governance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The world’s leading companies rely on Dataiku to operationalize AI and run it as a true business performance engine delivering measurable value. For more, visit the Dataiku &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.dataiku.com/?_gl=1*17edvf4*_ga*MjA1Mjk5NzY4OC4xNjY3MjMyMDUz*_ga_B3YXRYMY48*MTY2OTA1MDY5NS4xMi4xLjE2NjkwNTA2OTguNTcuMC4w&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/dataiku/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/dataiku&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/dataiku&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated Technical AI/ML/GenAI Partner Enablement Manager to join our growing Partner organisation at Dataiku. In this role, you will play a pivotal part in scaling our go-to-market capabilities by empowering our ecosystem of system integrators (SIs), consulting firms, cloud providers, independent software vendors (ISVs), and value-added resellers (VARs). As a key member of the Partner Enablement team, you will execute comprehensive enablement programs (including demonstrations, sales &amp;amp; technical pitches, hackathons, and more) to ensure our partners have the skills, tools, and knowledge needed to drive success with Dataiku&#39;s Universal AI platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have a strong technical background in Data Science, AI/ML, and/or GenAI, with a passion for helping partners become experts in utilising the Dataiku platform. You will be responsible for delivering impactful enablement initiatives that ensure Dataiku remains at the forefront of the AI, ML, and GenAI markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scope of Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Partner Enablement Manager will play a critical role in driving the readiness and productivity of Dataiku’s partner ecosystem across APJ. This role combines field-facing enablement leadership with deep collaboration across Partner Sales, Customer, and Revenue teams to ensure partners are fully capable of selling, implementing, and supporting Dataiku independently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the APJ theatre, the Partner Enablement Manager will support all partner types—including Global and Regional System Integrators, Resellers, Distributors, Tech Alliances, etc.—across sales, technical, and delivery enablement initiatives. The goal is to ensure partners can independently lead both pre-sales and post-sales cycles on behalf of Dataiku. This includes delivering targeted training programs, co-developing enablement plans aligned to regional priorities, and ensuring close collaboration with Dataiku’s Partner Sales and Field teams to accelerate partner-led revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Become a Dataiku Expert&lt;/strong&gt;: Deeply understand and master Dataiku&#39;s Universal AI platform to effectively educate, pitch, and demo the platform to new and existing partners.&amp;nbsp; Provide deep technical expertise and support to a set of assigned partners in assigned regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enableme

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dataiku.com/?utm_source=newswire&amp;amp;utm_medium=press-release&amp;amp;utm_campaign=PlatformforAISuccess&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Dataiku&lt;/a&gt; is the Platform for AI Success, the enterprise orchestration layer for building, deploying, and governing AI. In a single environment, teams design and operate analytics, machine learning, and AI agents with the transparency, collaboration, and control enterprises require. Sitting above data platforms, cloud infrastructure, and AI services, Dataiku connects the full enterprise AI stack — empowering organizations to run AI across multi-vendor environments with centralized governance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The world’s leading companies rely on Dataiku to operationalize AI and run it as a true business performance engine delivering measurable value. For more, visit the Dataiku &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.dataiku.com/?_gl=1*17edvf4*_ga*MjA1Mjk5NzY4OC4xNjY3MjMyMDUz*_ga_B3YXRYMY48*MTY2OTA1MDY5NS4xMi4xLjE2NjkwNTA2OTguNTcuMC4w&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/company/dataiku/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/dataiku&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/dataiku&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Business Development Representative to join our growing Central European Team As a Business Development Representative DACH. You will be responsible for driving Dataiku&#39;s business development activities. You must have the ability to understand the sales development process and technology stack and ensure its adoption. We are looking for a results-driven, hands-on self-starter, motivated to constantly improve and optimise the process to drive performance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Make An Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a large volume of daily inbound and outbound leads - connecting via phone, email and LinkedIn and qualifying them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with our Sales and Marketing executives to design, research and execute outbound vertical and/or geographical markets campaigns to grow sales pipeline in a dedicated territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with our Sales Executives to prospect and close large enterprise deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate and nurture early-phase prospects for potential future opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate knowledge of Dataiku DSS and its value proposition and an understanding of the Big Data ecosystem to converse with data and business leaders from SMB to high-growth companies, to large multinationals in industries such as e-commerce, retail, bank, insurance, utilities, and transport&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyse and report on your weekly activities to identify potential optimisations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Need To Be Successful&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal skills and excellent verbal and written communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have relevant experience and proven success in sales or business development in the software / tech industry or in a startup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to demonstrate organisational and project management skills with the ability to handle pressure and a high volume of tasks in a result-oriented environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly analytical and understand the need to track everything you do.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interested in innovative issues as Data Science and Predictive Analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business Level German&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
