&lt;p&gt;This role is focused on execution, content development, and program support within an established customer marketing strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work with customers and cross-functional teams to develop customer stories and marketing content for use across campaigns, sales, and communications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role requires equal parts content creator, customer advocate, and marketing program operator—someone who can not only develop great stories but also ensure those stories are activated across the business to drive measurable impact.&lt;/p&gt;
