&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Storytelling &amp;amp; Content Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop customer marketing content, including written case studies, executive narratives, testimonials, blog posts, and digital assets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner directly with customers and internal stakeholders to identify, capture, develop, and secure approval of compelling stories that demonstrate measurable business outcomes and business transformation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct customer interviews and translate complex technical and business achievements into engaging, audience-focused narratives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all customer-facing content meets Dataiku&#39;s standards for quality, accuracy, brand consistency, and regulatory compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a pipeline of customer stories aligned to defined content needs and priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Advocacy &amp;amp; Reference Activation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the growth and activation of Dataiku&#39;s customer advocacy ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruit and coordinate customer advocates in partnership with Customer Success, Account Teams, and Executive Sponsors.&lt;/li&gt;
