&lt;p&gt;Your role will be key in supporting the accelerated development of Dataiku in the Retail and CPG space and partnering with firms across the industry on their ambitious transformation trajectories. Your mission will run in tight partnership with all of Dataiku&#39;s key teams: Sales, Customer, Partnership, Product, and R&amp;amp;D.&lt;/p&gt;
