&lt;li&gt;Support the capitalization of internal knowledge and client experiences in the Retail and CPG space — adoption stories, use-cases — by developing relevant material to share internally and externally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support sales and customer activities targeting Retail and CPG firms; act as a key spokesperson with prospects and customers, and support executive engagement on this client segment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Boost Dataiku&#39;s visibility as a compelling thought-partner with Retail and CPG firms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other Industry Subject Matter Experts to expand our collective impact.&lt;/li&gt;
